episodes.title: Louis Theroux Exclusive Interview - My Scientology Movie
episodes.description:
Stefan Pape from HeyUGuys interviews documentary filmmaker Louis Theroux for his latest doc My Scientology Movie.

The movie premieres at London film festival 2015 and gives an in depth look at the My Scientology Movie. Stefan asks about whether Louis was followed during the making of the movie and since it was finished, how the idea to do a documentary around the topic came up and if he'll ever return to the topic again.
